org.activebpel.rt.bpel.def.validation.expr
Class AeExpressionValidationResult

java.lang.Object
  org.activebpel.rt.bpel.def.validation.expr.AeExpressionValidationResult
All Implemented Interfaces:
IAeExpressionValidationResult
public class AeExpressionValidationResult
extends java.lang.Object
implements IAeExpressionValidationResult

Implements a simple expression validation result object. This implementation of the IAeExpressionValidationResult interface is basically just a container for the various lists required by the interface.
